  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel has a generous hot and cold buffet breakfast every day.</p>
<p>Evening meals take place in the hotel's restaurant where you'll enjoy a delicious three-course menu.</p>
<p>You can choose to splash out and accompany your meals with a wide range of excellent wines - both regional and from all around the world.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year four course gala dinners are included.</p>
<p>If you fancy something different, try out the hotel's fine dining a la carte restaurant which specialises in Valdostana dishes, payable locally.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
