  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>sleep two people and are around 18m². They have a balcony with views facing from the back of the hotel.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Room</strong><strong>s </strong>sleep two people and are 18m². They have incredible panoramic views from the balcony at the front of the hotel.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Lodges </strong>sleep up to four people and are made up of two connecting Deluxe Rooms.</p>
<p><strong>Suites </strong>sleep up to three people and are a spacious 36m². These rooms have a balcony with a mountain view and are available on request, please call us to book.</p>
<p><strong>Superior and Deluxe Rooms for sole use</strong> are available for a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
